ComicInfo.Title: Fit the Fifth: How Doth the Little Crocodile...?
ComicInfo.Summary: Brand New Arc! Great For New Readers! Roger Langridge - the Harvey Award winner behind The Muppet Show and Thor: The Mighty Avenger - begins the second arc of his critically acclaimed side-splitting adventure! The journey continues as Princess Scarlett, baby Rusty, the Walrus and the Carpenter, and the fearless Snarkhunter Crew hit the high seas in search of the missing Red King. Swashbuckling, laughs, crocodiles - this issue has it all!
